            "title": "港股開跌133點   國泰跌3%   東方海外挫近3.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數開報25583， 跌133點或0.52%  ; 恒生科技指數開報5006，跌21點或0.42% ; 恒生國企指數開報8670，跌28點或0.33%。   </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交43.33億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"國泰航空\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_國泰_source-web-.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"國泰航空\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_國泰_source-web-.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">國泰航空</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">太古(00019)折讓9.6%配售國泰航空(00293)，國泰航空開跌3%，報12.6元，成交居首，太古升4.11%，報86.15元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融股受壓，友邦(01299)跌1.22%，報83.3元 ; 滙控(00005)跌2.41%，報125.8元，集團暫關閉卡塔爾分行 ; 渣打(02888)跌1.1%，報171.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中海油(00883)升1.38%，報29.5元，為歷史高 ; 中石油(00857)升1.22%，報10.75元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">東方海外(00316)挫3.44%，報148.9元，盈利下滑末期息減逾68%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">申洲((02313)跌1.43%，報55元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">理想汽車(02015)跌1.71%，報68.95元，去年非公認準則純利跌77.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15736546-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c133%e9%bb%9e-%e5%9c%8b%e6%b3%b0%e8%b7%8c3-%e6%9d%b1%e6%96%b9%e6%b5%b7%e5%a4%96%e6%8c%ab%e8%bf%913-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240420240415_FI_source-web_HKSTOCK.png.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 09:32:41",
